channel.title: Product Update - June '19
channel.description:
This month, with the newest release, we changed the name of Core to Engine. Plus, we updated the Engine to v0.10, plus added a a new CLI and JS library v3.0.0!

This is a companion discussion topic for the original entry at https://blog.mesg.com/mesg-product-update-july-2019/
